combining form of [[महत्]] (mahat) "great" + [[राष्ट्र]] (rāśt'ra) "kingdom".
===Noun===
'''महाराष्ट्र''' (Mahārāśt'ra)

# [[Maharashtra]], a state of [[India]], having [[Mumbai]] ([[Bombay]]) as its capital.

